    <p>Current-generation Café wall ovens include most of the premium-tier feature set: True European Convection (third-element system), SmartHQ Wi-Fi integration, Air Fry mode. The differentiation from Profile is at finish + hardware rather than feature-technology level. Service infrastructure shares Haier-owned GE Appliances Louisville Kentucky distribution; common Café parts 2-4 day lead, specialty Café-specific finishes quoted individually through specialty-parts channel.</p>
